  "prompt": "Did crimes shown by Savdhan India, Crime Patrol, and other similar shows real?",
  "response": "\"Savdhan India,\" \"Crime Patrol,\" and similar crime shows are primarily intended to entertain and inform the audience by dramatizing real-life crime cases. While many episodes are inspired by actual events, the stories are often fictionalized to some extent for dramatic effect. This means that while the core of a story might be based on true incidents, the details, characters, and dialogue are often altered or enhanced for storytelling purposes. These shows aim to raise awareness about crime and encourage viewers to be cautious and vigilant in their daily lives.",
